<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-primary">
        <a href="/" class="navbar-brand">
            PHILIPE
        </a>
        <ul class="navbar-nav mr-auto">
            <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a>
                </li>
            {%for category in categories%}
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/category/{{category.slug}}">{{category.title}}</a>
                </li>
            {%endfor%}
        </ul>
    </nav>
    <div class="container">
        {%block content%}
        <hr>
        <div class="jumbotron">
            <h1 class="display-4">Bem vindo!</h1>
            <p class="lead">Este Ã© um simples blog desenvolvido por mim.</p>
            <hr class="my-4">
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Adipisci dolor aspernatur quisquam sapiente voluptatum! Exercitationem vero quisquam, similique soluta animi culpa voluptatem, impedit eos, veritatis minima sapiente molestiae aliquid sint..</p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="#" role="button">Learn more</a>
        </div>
        <hr>
        {%for article in articles%}
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h2>{{article.title}}</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                <a href="/{{article.slug}}" class="btn btn-success">Ler artigo</a>
                </div>
            </div><br>
        {%endfor%}
        {%endblock%}
    </div>

    <script src="/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/tinymce/tinymce.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>